          "description": "I came here for two weeks to train in intestinal ultrasound. What I didn\u2019t realize is that NYU IBD center is very well run, delivering state of the art care to its patients. The staff including the providers are very kind and knowledgeable. The facilities are brand new. What I love is the patient centered feel. It is rare to be able to get your doctor appointment, lab, ultrasound and infusion all in one office! Kudos to the NYU team.",
