          "description": "Changed my life. I switched here because I was having a terrible flare up and my last doctor seemed unconcerned and wouldn't make any changes to my medication. I started seeing Dr. Holmer and she has been fantastic. She got right to helping me figure out a medication that works for me and had continued to be proactive and involved. All the nurses and techs have also been extremely kind and remember me each time I come in for my infusion. This place has made a huge positive impact on my life.",
