          "description": "The doctors here are great but one of the front desk receptionists is a nightmare. She is extremely rude and gives you attitude every time. She clearly hates her job and projects that hate on you. At the beginning of 2026, I gave her my new insurance card. I also asked her clearly whether or not my new insurance is accepted here. She just snapped at me and barked yes, without checking. A couple days later, I got an enormous bill for my appointment. This is ridiculous. I don\u2019t know if she failed to add my insurance or if this office does not accept my new insurance. Now I have a big mess to clean up and possibly a crazy bill to pay. ALL of this could have been avoided if this lady just did her job, by checking and adding my insurance card. Why be a receptionist if you cannot even handle an insurance card?! All she does is sit there angrily and snap at people. LOVE the doctors here but dealing with that front desk is not worth it.",
