          "description": "I never got to go here. I don't understand the point of being this \"great\" IBD center if they won't help diagnose complicated cases. I have a long GI history and several Dr's have told me to go to an IBD specialist so I tried this place and I can't because I don't have a confirmed diagnosis even though their website in several places say they diagnose. One of the dumbest things I've ever heard.",
