          "description": "They only treat already diagnosed IBD cases. I was told they don\u2019t take cases that require complex diagnosis which is surprising for what\u2019s supposed to be a comprehensive IBD center",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKUVpWTllkMjlVZW1kNllUY3lPV1J6T0c1ZmNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xe3fdf480424a2cc!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkJQZVNYd29Uemd6YTcyOWRzOG5fcUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
